Installation with CocoaPods
#


Installation with 
CocoaPods
 is an alternative to downloading the SDK. CocoaPods is a dependency manager for iOS and Mac apps, which automates and simplifies the process of using 3rd-party libraries in your projects.


pod 'SpotX-SDK'




